name: Nonneg.nat_floor_coe
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝¹ : OrderedSemiring α
inst✝ : FloorSemiring α
a : Subtype fun r => LE.le 0 r
⊢ Eq (Nat.floor ↑a) (Nat.floor a)
decl:
@[norm_cast]
theorem nat_floor_coe [OrderedSemiring α] [FloorSemiring α] (a : { r : α // 0 ≤ r }) :
    ⌊(a : α)⌋₊ = ⌊a⌋₊ :=
  rfl
